---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="AI Privacy Gateway — 永久免费开源"
  description="AI Privacy Gateway 基于 MIT 许可证永久免费开源。个人和商业项目均可自由使用。"
  canonicalURL="https://privacygw.pages.dev/pricing">
  <Nav />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <span class="badge-dot"></span>
        <span>永久免费 · MIT 开源</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        完全<span class="gradient-text">免费</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-description">
        AI Privacy Gateway 基于 MIT 许可证开源，永久免费。<br/>
        个人和商业项目均可自由使用，无需激活。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/download" class="btn btn-primary">立即下载</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway" class="btn btn-ghost">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features included -->
  <section class="features-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Lite 版包含全部核心功能</h2>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-card glass">
          <h3>智能脱敏引擎</h3>
          <p>正则 + NER 双引擎，14 类敏感实体自动识别</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card glass">
          <h3>流式 SSE 代理</h3>
          <p>完美代理流式响应，实时脱敏/还原，零延迟感知</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card glass">
          <h3>本地加密存储</h3>
          <p>SQLite 本地存储，映射数据永不离开你的机器</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card glass">
          <h3>自定义敏感词</h3>
          <p>支持正则 + 关键词自定义脱敏规则</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card glass">
          <h3>管理后台</h3>
          <p>实时统计面板，查看脱敏次数、实体分布、映射记录</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card glass">
          <h3>全平台覆盖</h3>
          <p>Docker / Windows / macOS / pip / 浏览器扩展</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">常见问题</h2>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-card glass">
          <h3>Lite 版真的完全免费吗？</h3>
          <p>是的，基于 MIT 许可证开源，永久免费。没有隐藏费用，不需要激活。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-card glass">
          <h3>可以商用吗？</h3>
          <p>可以。MIT 许可证允许自由用于个人和商业项目，包括闭源商业产品。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-card glass">
          <h3>数据安全吗？</h3>
          <p>所有数据存储在本地 SQLite 数据库中，不会上传到任何第三方服务器。网关运行在你自己的机器上，完全由你掌控。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-card glass">
          <h3>如何获取支持？</h3>
          <p>通过 <a href="https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway/issues">GitHub Issues</a> 提交问题，或查阅 <a href="/docs">文档</a>。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 10rem 0 4rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-content {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .badge-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; }
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    color: var(--primary);
    background: rgba(134, 239, 172, 0.05);
  }

  .features-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .feature-card {
    padding: 1.75rem;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .faq-section {
    padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
  }

  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .faq-card h3 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .faq-card a {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title { font-size: 2.25rem; }
    .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 400px; }
    .faq-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
